Class FSMStateFunctionBuilder<S,D,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.persistence.fsm.japi.pf.FSMStateFunctionBuilder<S,D,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the state type
    D - the data type
    E - the domain event type

    public class FSMStateFunctionBuilder<S,D,E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder used to create a partial function for FSM.whenUnhandled(scala.PartialFunction<akka.actor.FSM.Event<D>, akka.actor.FSM.State<S, D>>).
